'''Occupy Cal''' is an ongoing series of [[Demonstration (people)|demonstrations]] in Berkeley based in the [[University of California, Berkeley]] in [[Sproul Plaza]]. It started on November 9, 2011, in protest of the possible budget increases the UC Regents on which they will vote on November 16, 2011. It is an offshoot of the [[Occupy Wall Street]] movement.
